# Project Structure

The structure of this project is as follows:

```
public: Assets that should not be managed or optimized by Astro.
- admin: DecapCMS admin folder.
  - config.yml: DecapCMS configuration.
specs: Functional and nonfunctional requirements.
src: The source code of the site.
- assets: Contains assets (images and stuff) managed by DecapCMS.
- components: Contains Astro components.
  - common: Reusable components across the different pages.
    - index.ts: Used to re-export components.
  - page-specific: Components specific to one page.
- content: Data and textual content that goes onto the site.
- layouts: Astro layouts.
  - SitePageLayout.ts: The default layout.
- pages: The actual Astro pages of the site.
- styles: Site CSS.
  - global.css: The default, always included CSS file.
- util: Helper code and logic.
  - assets.ts: Loading image files from the assets directory.
  - links.ts: Navigation-related stuff, so we don't have to type out the URLs again and again.
  - markdown.ts: Markdown rendering. 
```
